```

Original `<PLACEHOLDER>`: `} else if (part_count_diff == -1) {`

So the original code structure is:
```
if (part_count_diff == 0) { return "samelevel" }
else if (part_count_diff == 1) {
    // EMPTY - the placeholder IS the closing brace + next else if
